<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">There are authorized to be appropriated to carry out this subchapter such sums as may be necessary for fiscal year 2007.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idb937c5c4-5e84-11f1-a692-ec26948f6fea">(<ref href="/us/pl/117/286/s3/c">Pub. L. 117–286, § 3(c)</ref>, <date date="2022-12-27">Dec. 27, 2022</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/136/4302">136 Stat. 4302</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
