<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Although provisions authorizing the appropriation of “such sums as may be necessary” are generally considered unnecessary, and although this provision is obsolete because it explicitly applies only to fiscal year 2007, the provision is nevertheless intentionally restated in chapter 131 of title 5, United States Code.</p>
